title: Cybersecurity Firm’s Strategy Raises Eyebrows
text:
Cybersecurity firm FireEye Inc. has cleaned up large data breaches at Sony Pictures Entertainment, Anthem Inc. and Home Depot Inc. Its computers and software help General Electric Co., Facebook Inc. and the National Security Agency keep out hackers.
